(353, '2013-06-01 20:52:54.000000', 'Finanzas', 'finanzas', '<p><strong>Nuestra política de Transparencia en la Gestión nos lleva a hacer públicos y poner a disposición de todas las personas interesadas los Balances Financieros - Contables de Educación, Ambiente y Territorio.</strong></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"images/Balance%202012.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Ver Balance 2012:</strong> <img src=\"/media/images/stories/noticias-portada/transparencia/flecha%20ver.png\" border=\"0\" /></a><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/viewer?url=http://eatnea.org/images/Balance%25202012.pdf&amp;embedded=false&amp;chrome=false&amp;dov=1\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"View this &quot;pdf&quot; file\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 3px;\" /></a><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/viewer?url=http://eatnea.org/images/stories/noticias-portada/transparencia/balance%2520eat%25202011.pdf&amp;embedded=false&amp;chrome=false&amp;dov=1\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"View this &quot;pdf&quot; file\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 3px;\" /></a></span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">A continuación se puden ver los balances de los ejercios: 2007 / 2008 / 2009 / 2010 / 2011</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<table style=\"width: 468px; height: 71px;\" border=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Ver Balance 2007 / 2008</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Ver Balance 2009</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Ver Balance 2010</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Ver Balance 2011</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"images/stories/noticias-portada/transparencia/balance_eat_2007-2008.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/media/images/stories/gifs%20animados%20flechas%20104.png\" border=\"0\" /></a><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/viewer?url=http://eatnea.org/images/storie